jnxEventTrap.name: jnxEventTrap
jnxEventTrap.description: Notification generated by op-script or event-policies. Apart from the jnxEventTrap objects, this notification can include one or more attribute-value pairs. The attribute-value pairs shall be identified by objects jnxEventAvAttribute and jnxEventAvValue.
